1. Decide which business to order pizza from.
2. Decide which of the business' locations to order from.
3. Decide which kinds of pizza to order.
4. Decide the quantity of each kind of pizza to order.
5. Decide how the pizzas will be recieved (delivery or pickup)
6. Decide how the pizzas will be paid for.
7. Submit a request to the business location based on information from steps 1-6.